    "description_long": "This is a black pickup truck with a robust, utilitarian design, featuring a front grille with a gold Chevrolet bowtie emblem and two prominent circular fog lights. The vehicle has a two-door cab and a spacious open cargo bed at the rear, which is partially covered by a large silver toolbox. The wheels are large with rugged, multi-spoke rims, and the tires appear suitable for both urban and light off-road use. The side mirrors are angular and extend outward, and a long antenna is mounted on the passenger side. The truck's body is primarily black, with some metallic and wooden textures visible near the cargo bed area. The rear of the truck is simple, with red tail lights and a visible bumper.",
